➜欲阻特朗普推迟选举念头 白宫宣布：大选将在11月3日举行
http://dwnews.com/-/60206370	242
<div class="sc-bdVaJa jLaXBp"><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">美国白宫办公厅主任梅多斯（Mark Meadows）8月2日表示，美国将于11月3日举行大选。</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB"><strong class="s1wvug8s-0 bbEmvD">美国新冠肺炎疫情持续严峻，面对即将到来的大选，美国总统特朗普压力山大（点击浏览高清图）：</strong></p><div class="sc-bwzfXH liBCIH sc-bdVaJa hjfdHC"><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa jHRAtr"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa jHRAtr"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa SmPPj"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-2 kxqYmT sc-cJSrbW ipLTMg sc-TOsTZ gJBPed"><div class="sc-gqjmRU jWuFDX">+<!-- -->15</div></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-2 kxqYmT sc-cJSrbW ipLTMg sc-TOsTZ gJBPed"><div class="sc-gqjmRU jWuFDX">+<!-- -->14</div></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-2 kxqYmT sc-cJSrbW ipLTMg 