<div class="sc-bdVaJa jLaXBp"><div class="s1cpgqaz-0 gtFIdP sc-bdVaJa gElGvB"><p class="s1cpgqaz-1 iRTWry sc-gqjmRU jTjJUk">美国媒体8月1日引述共和党全国代表大会发言人称，根据北卡罗来纳州因应新型冠状病毒肺炎（COVID-19）而颁布的限制措施，大会将秘密举行，谢绝传媒参与。共和党全国委员会（RNC）一名匿名官员则强调，他们尚未做出任何最终决定。</p></div><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">最先报道这个消息的媒体是《阿肯色州民主党人公报 》（Arkansas Democrat-Gazette）。美联社引述这名发言人称：“鉴于北卡罗来纳州的健康限制和局限性，我们正计划关闭8月21日周五至8月24日周一夏洛特活动新闻（环节）。”</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB"><strong class="s1wvug8s-0 bbEmvD">↓↓↓想看选举重要日子，请点击放大观看：</strong></p><div class="view-tracker"></div><div class="sc-bwzfXH hUbGFF sc-bdVaJa cVbOod"><div class="s59kcgq-0 gIXiEP sc-bdVaJa eEfiTB"><div class="LazyLoad" style="height:100%;width:100%"></div></div><div class="s59kcgq-0 gIXiEP sc-bdVaJa eEfiTB"><div class="LazyLoad" style="height:100%;width:100%"></div></div></div><div class="sc-bwzfXH liBCIH sc-bdVaJa hjfdHC"><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa YQcII"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa YQcII"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-2 kxqYmT sc-cJSrbW ipLTMg sc-TOsTZ gJBPed"><div class="sc-gqjmRU jWuFDX">+<!-- -->2</div></div></