<div class="sc-bdVaJa jLaXBp"><div class="s1cpgqaz-0 gtFIdP sc-bdVaJa gElGvB"><p class="s1cpgqaz-1 iRTWry sc-gqjmRU jTjJUk">英国北部一些地区的新型冠状病毒肺炎（COVID-19）确诊个案有所增加后，曼彻斯特（Manchester）市政厅议长莱瑟（Richard Leese）8月2日称，当地已宣布发生重大事件。</p></div><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">莱瑟指：“虽然市议会和合作伙伴组织自今年初以来一直密切合作以应对疫情大流行的影响，（但）宣布重大事件意味着我们可以进一步加大这个力度。”</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">他又指，“它允许（当地）建立一个中央指挥机构来监督（疫情）反应，并让相关机构可以利用额外的资源（来抗疫）。”</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">▼<strong class="s1wvug8s-0 bbEmvD">想知道其他国家民众在疫情持续期间的生活？请点击放大观看：</strong></p><div class="view-tracker"></div><div class="sc-bwzfXH hUbGFF sc-bdVaJa cVbOod"><div class="s59kcgq-0 gIXiEP sc-bdVaJa eEfiTB"><div class="LazyLoad" style="height:100%;width:100%"></div></div><div class="s59kcgq-0 gIXiEP sc-bdVaJa eEfiTB"><div class="LazyLoad" style="height:100%;width:100%"></div></div></div><div class="sc-bwzfXH liBCIH sc-bdVaJa hjfdHC"><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa jHRAtr"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa jHRAtr"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa SmPPj"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-2 kxqYmT sc-cJSrbW ipLTMg sc-TOsTZ gJBPed"><div class=