<div class="sc-bdVaJa jLaXBp"><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">中印边境局势依然紧张，两军并没有完全脱离接触。在8月2日的中印军方高层对话中，印度要求中国撤军，但是谈判似乎没有带来突破。</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">印度亚洲通讯社8月3日报道称，第5轮中印军队指挥官级别的谈判于8月2日晚上21时30分结束。这次会议在实控线（LAC）中方一侧的摩尔多（Moldo）举行。</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">消息人士说，这次会晤持续了超过10小时，印方在会议中提到了印度军队和中国军队在班公错湖（Pangong Tso）地区脱离接触问题。</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB"><strong class="s1wvug8s-0 bbEmvD">印防长赴前线观看军演，称谈判未必能解决问题（点击图集浏览）：</strong></p><div class="sc-bwzfXH liBCIH sc-bdVaJa hjfdHC"><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa jHRAtr"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa jHRAtr"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa SmPPj"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-2 kxqYmT sc-cJSrbW ipLTMg sc-TOsTZ gJBPed"><div class="sc-gqjmRU jWuFDX">+<!-- -->6</div></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-2 kxqYmT sc-cJSrbW ipLTMg sc-TOsTZ gJBPed"><div class="sc-gqjmRU jWuFDX">+<!-- -->5</div></div></div></div></d