div><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">财长努钦（Steven Mnuchin）反指是民主党问题。他指出，共和党提出延长600美元失业金一周，以便谈判寻求共识，但民主党人却拒绝谈判。</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">美国财经杂志《福布斯》（Forbes）分析，接下来较可能出现的结局是，两党经协商后推出金额统一的失业救济金作为短期发放之用，金额可能在每周200美元至600美元之间，或者是规订金额会随时间逐渐缩减。</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">▼<strong class="s1wvug8s-0 bbEmvD">想知道其他国家民众在疫情持续期间的生活？请点击放大观看：</strong></p><div class="view-tracker"></div><div class="sc-bwzfXH liBCIH sc-bdVaJa hjfdHC"><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa jHRAtr"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa jHRAtr"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa SmPPj"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-2 kxqYmT sc-cJSrbW ipLTMg sc-TOsTZ gJBPed"><div class="sc-gqjmRU jWuFDX">+<!-- -->3</div></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-2 kxqYmT sc-cJSrbW ipLTMg sc-TOsTZ gJBPed"><div class="sc-gqjmRU jWuFDX">+<!-- -->2</div></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 ing