➜【新冠肺炎】世卫：武汉不一定是病毒出现跨物种传播之地
http://dwnews.com/-/60206510	57301
<div class="sc-bdVaJa jLaXBp"><div class="s1cpgqaz-0 gtFIdP sc-bdVaJa gElGvB"><p class="s1cpgqaz-1 iRTWry sc-gqjmRU jTjJUk">世界卫生组织（WHO）突发卫生事件规划执行主任瑞安（Mike Ryan）8月3日指出，武汉有就非典型肺炎专设监测系统并发布预警，但并不一定意味着武汉就是新型冠状病毒肺炎（COVID-19）出现跨物种传播的地点。</p></div><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">瑞安表示，中国科学家已提供他们在华南海鲜市场调查的资料，WHO及中国已同意有必要进行更深入的调查，以确定疫情爆发的源头。</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">中国外交部7月13日称世卫专家已抵达北京。瑞安称他们尚未回来，故未有机会听取他们汇报。</p><div class="view-tracker"></div><div class="sc-bwzfXH hUbGFF sc-bdVaJa cVbOod"><div class="s59kcgq-0 gIXiEP sc-bdVaJa eEfiTB"><div class="LazyLoad" style="height:100%;width:100%"></div></div><div class="s59kcgq-0 gIXiEP sc-bdVaJa eEfiTB"><div class="LazyLoad" style="height:100%;width:100%"></div></div></div><div class="sc-bdVaJa hVSRSV"><div class="sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="wad570-1 cxYulZ sc-bdVaJa bkDnMq"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div><p class="wad570-0 oppUq sc-gqjmRU hrgbln">图为6月25日世卫总干事谭德塞在瑞士日内瓦出席新闻发布会。（Reuters）</p></div></div><div class="view-tracker"></div><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">▼<strong class="s1wvug8s-0 bbEmvD">想知道其他国家民众在疫情持续期间的生活？请点击放大观看：</strong></p><div class="view-tracker"></div><div class="sc-bwzfXH liBCIH sc-bdVaJa hjfdHC"><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa jHRAtr"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa jHRAtr"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa SmPPj"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div></div></div><div class="s1xnqz7c-3 gjtFLz sc-bdVaJa ekKPF"><div class="s1xnqz7c-0 inguzk sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><div class="s1xnqz7c-1 kzheUZ"><div style="h