 class="s2jnsig-0 hZOstq sc-gqjmRU rgrzA"><span class="rfg5jk-0 hghSag s3n5kh1-0 gcPAtQ sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><a class="sc-htoDjs hbsase" href="/中国/60206448/新冠肺炎疫苗是否安全中美双方专家各执一词" target="_blank">新冠肺炎疫苗是否安全 中美双方专家各执一词<span class="view-tracker-inline"></span></a></span></div></div><div class="view-tracker"></div><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB"><strong class="s1wvug8s-0 bbEmvD">谭德塞：目前没“万灵丹”</strong></p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">谭德塞又警告，目前许多新冠疫苗均处于第3阶段临床试验，各国都希望拥有许多有效预防感染的疫苗，然而，此刻没有“万灵丹”，而且可能永远不会有。 </p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">谭德塞及瑞安呼吁所有国家严格地执行防疫措施，包括戴口罩、保持社交距离、洗手以及进行病毒检测。</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB">他在同一场合建议染疫的妈妈继续喂哺母乳，称此举好处大于感染风险。</p><p class="q8eose-0 jFVFTo sc-gqjmRU gBjLGB"><strong class="s1wvug8s-0 bbEmvD">推荐阅读：</strong></p><div class="view-tracker"></div><div class="sc-bdVaJa hVSRSV"><div class="s2jnsig-0 hZOstq sc-gqjmRU rgrzA"><span class="rfg5jk-0 hghSag s3n5kh1-0 gcPAtQ sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><a class="sc-htoDjs hbsase" href="/香港/60206009/社论港版国安法雷霆落地接下来需要惠风细雨" target="_blank">社论：港版国安法雷霆落地 接下来需要惠风细雨<span class="view-tracker-inline"></span></a></span></div><div class="s2jnsig-0 hZOstq sc-gqjmRU rgrzA"><span class="rfg5jk-0 hghSag s3n5kh1-0 gcPAtQ sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><a class="sc-htoDjs hbsase" href="/中国/60206326/人事观察李克强内阁换血未能一步到位" target="_blank">【人事观察】李克强内阁换血未能一步到位<span class="view-tracker-inline"></span></a></span></div><div class="s2jnsig-0 hZOstq sc-gqjmRU rgrzA"><span class="rfg5jk-0 hghSag s3n5kh1-0 gcPAtQ sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><a class="sc-htoDjs hbsase" href="/台湾/60206136/多维TW从香港的沉寂看台湾的喧嚣" target="_blank">【多维TW】从香港的沉寂看台湾的喧嚣<span class="view-tracker-inline"></span></a></span></div><div class="s2jnsig-0 hZOstq sc-gqjmRU rgrzA"><span class="rfg5jk-0 hghSag s3n5kh1-0 gcPAtQ sc-bdVaJa iHZvIS"><a class="sc-htoDjs hbsase" href="/台湾/60206433/被美国剥好几层皮蔡英文是否还要签台美FTA" target="_blank">被美国剥好几层皮 蔡英文是否还要签台美FTA<span class="view-tracker-inline"></span></a></span></div><div class="s2jnsig-0 hZOstq sc-gqjmRU rgrzA"><span 